graph LR
    ModelMesh[ModelMesh Serving Operator]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    ModelMesh -->|model metadata<br/>HTTP/2379| etcd[etcd v3.5.4+<br/>Required]
    ModelMesh -->|model artifacts<br/>HTTPS/443 or HTTP/9000| S3[S3-compatible Storage<br/>Required]
    ModelMesh -->|CRD watch/mgmt<br/>HTTPS/443| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server<br/>Required]
    ModelMesh -->|metrics protection<br/>HTTPS/8443| RBACProxy[kube-rbac-proxy<br/>Required]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional)
    ModelMesh -.->|TLS certs<br/>K8s API| CertManager[cert-manager v1.0+<br/>Optional]
    ModelMesh -.->|metrics scraping<br/>HTTPS/8443, HTTP/2112| Prometheus[Prometheus Operator v0.50+<br/>Optional]

    %% Internal RHOAI/ODH Dependencies (Container Images)
    ModelMesh -->|runtime image| ModelMeshRuntime[kserve/modelmesh<br/>Java Runtime<br/>Internal Image]
    ModelMesh -->|adapter image| RuntimeAdapterImage[kserve/modelmesh-runtime-adapter<br/>Go Service<br/>Internal Image]
    ModelMesh -->|proxy image| RESTProxyImage[kserve/rest-proxy<br/>Go Service<br/>Internal Image]

    %% Model Server Runtime Images
    ModelMesh -->|runtime backend| Triton[Triton Inference Server<br/>nvcr.io/nvidia/tritonserver<br/>External Runtime]
    ModelMesh -->|runtime backend| MLServer[MLServer 1.x<br/>kserve/mlserver<br/>External Runtime]
    ModelMesh -->|runtime backend| OVMS[OpenVINO Model Server 1.x<br/>openvino/model_server<br/>External Runtime]
    ModelMesh -->|runtime backend| TorchServe[TorchServe 0.x<br/>pytorch/torchserve<br/>External Runtime]

    %% Integration Points (Optional/Consuming)
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard] -.->|UI management| ModelMesh
    Pipelines[Data Science Pipelines] -.->|auto deployment| ModelMesh

    %% Service Mesh (Optional Integration)
    ServiceMesh[Service Mesh/Istio] -.->|mTLS, AuthZ| ModelMesh

